'''Hwang Kyeong-tae''' ({{korean|황경태}}; born August 17, 1996) is South Korean professional baseball [[infielder]] who is currently playing for the [[Doosan Bears]] of [[Korea Baseball Organization]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.koreabaseball.com/Record/Player/HitterDetail/Basic.aspx?playerId=66207|title=KBO 홈페이지 player info|last=스포츠투아이|first=|date=|website=|language=ko|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2018-05-09}}</ref> His major position is [[shortstop]], however, he sometimes plays as [[second baseman]] or [[third baseman]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://osen.mt.co.kr/article/G1110653135|title=[오!쎈 인터뷰] '수비 극찬' 황경태 "제 2의 김재호가 꿈"|access-date=2018-05-09|language=ko}}</ref> He graduated from Daegu Sangwon High School and was selected for the Doosan Bears by a draft in 2016 (2nd draft, 2nd round).<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2015092414313949452&outlink=1&ref=https://search.naver.com|title=두산 베어스, 2차 지명 신인선수 계약 완료- 스타뉴스|date=2015-09-24|work=스타뉴스|access-date=2018-05-09|language=ko-KR}}</ref>
