{{Infobox football biography | name = Mohamed Chamité | image = | image_size = | fullname = Mohamed Abderrahmane Chamité | birth_date = | birth_place = [[Comoros]] | height = | currentclub = | clubnumber = | position = | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = | years1 = | clubs1 = | caps1 = | goals1 = | years2 = | clubs2 = | caps2 = | goals2 = | years3 = | clubs3 = | caps3 = | goals3 = | nationalyears1 = | nationalteam1 = | nationalcaps1 = | nationalgoals1 = | manageryears1 = 2010–2011 | managerclubs1 = [[Comoros national football team|Comoros]] | manageryears2 = | managerclubs2 = | pcupdate = | ntupdate = }}
'''Mohamed Abderrahmane Chamité''' is a [[Comoros|Comorian]] professional [[association football manager|football manager]].
==Career== Since September 2010 until September 2011 he coached the [[Comoros national football team]].<ref>[http://www.national-football-teams.com/country/222/2011/Comoros.html Mohamed Abderrahmane Chamité at National-Football-Teams.com]</ref><ref>[http://comores.exprimanoo.com/articles/footballchamiteun-homme-a-poigne-pour-un-challenge-de-taille-1406.htm Football : Chamité, un homme à poigne pour un challenge de taille, Sport, Comores]</ref>
