{{Infobox football biography |name = Sandro Tau |fullname = Sandro Manu Tau |birth_date = {{birth date and age|1997|4|30|df=y}} |birth_place = [[Tahiti]] |height = |position = [[Midfielder (association football)|Midfielder]] |currentclub = [[AS Pirae]] |clubnumber = 14 |youthyears1 = |youthclubs1 = |years1 = 2015–2017 |clubs1 = [[AS Tiare Tahiti]] |years2 = 2017- |clubs2 = [[AS Pirae]] |caps2 = |goals2 = |years3 = |clubs3 = |caps3 = |goals3 = |nationalyears1= 2016 |nationalteam1= [[Tahiti national under-20 football team|Tahiti U20]] |nationalcaps1= 2 |nationalgoals1= 1 |nationalyears2= 2018– |nationalteam2= [[Tahiti national football team|Tahiti]] |nationalcaps2= 2 |nationalgoals2= 0 }} '''Sandro Tau''' (born 30 April 1997) is a [[Tahiti]]an [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder (association football)|midfielder]] for Tahitian club [[AS Pirae]] and the [[Tahiti national football team|Tahiti national team]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oceaniafootball.com/competition-list/friendly-match-football-male-a-432317/tahiti-new-caledonia-5038310/|title=Friendly match: Tahiti - New Caledonia|author=OFC football|date=|website=Oceaniafootballcom|accessdate=27 March 2018}}</ref>
==Club career== Tau started his career in the youth of [[AS Tiare Tahiti]]. In 2015 he moved to the first team and made his debut. In 2017 he moved to Tahitian powerhouse [[AS Pirae]].
==International career== In 2018 Tau was called up by [[Naea Bennett]] for the [[Tahiti national football team]] to play two friendly games against [[New Caledonia]]. He made his debut on March 21, 2017 in a 0-0 draw against [[New Caledonia national football team|New Caledonia]] when he enter the field in the 70th minute of play, replacing [[Yohann Tihoni]].
